Package org.jmisb.api.klv.st1904 Description

ST 1904 Motion Imagery Metadata (MIMD): Base Attributes.

ST 1901, ST 1902, ST 1903, ST 1904, ST 1905, ST 1906, ST 1907 and ST 1908 collectively define Motion Imagery Metadata (MIMD). ST 1904 defines the MIMD Base Attributes, which comprises a common set of attributes supporting all classes across the suite of MIMD standards.

Implementation note: Most of the implementation of this document is generated from the Motion Imagery Modeling Language (MIML) representation.
